author: Nerdstalgic
description:
Tom Cruise may just be the last true movie star in Hollywood. With a career spanning decades, Cruise has delivered Oscar-worthy performances, record-breaking blockbusters, and jaw-dropping stunts that most actors wouldn’t dream of attempting.

From Top Gun to Jerry Maguire, and most iconically, Mission: Impossible — Tom Cruise has redefined what it means to be a leading man in modern cinema. As we approach the end of his Mission: Impossible run, it’s clear: Tom Cruise isn’t just playing Ethan Hunt—he is Ethan Hunt.

#tomcruise #missionimpossible #missionimpossibledeadreckoning #nerdstalgic
title: Is Tom Cruise The Last Irreplaceable Movie Star?
